#eNCA #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Operation Dudula leader Nhlanhla 'Lux' Mohlauli says there's a witch hunt against him. He handed himself over to the police in Soweto on Wednesday, in connection with a common assault case from around three years ago. His arrest comes weeks after he was released on a bail on a housebreaking charge. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has the story in the video above.